  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.4.5">
<l>ivaḷirāp pakalvāy verīitaṉa</l>
<l>kuvaḷaiyoṇ kaṇṇanīr koṇṭāḷvaṇṭu</l>
<l>tivaḷuntaṇ ṇantuḻāy koṭī reṉa</l>
<l>tavaḷa vaṇṇar takavukaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>This one, speaking incoherently night [and] day,</l>
<l>she has water in her water-lily bright eyes.</l>
<l>Saying “give [me] the cool Tulsi touched by bees,</l>
<l>are [these actions] befitting those of white colour?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
